name: R.O.B.O.T. (Regressive Organism Born Of Trash)
description: This is my first "personal" piece. My origin story. It deals with the topic of hoarding, a phenomenon I experienced growing up in a hoarder's home. When the person who should be taking care of you is attached to their belongings, it is easy to feel discarded in an ugly, confusing, and dirty world. It took me a long time to get free and realize that there was light within me, and that it had always been there.
